@startuml A3_02_component_enrollment_database_simple
title Enrollment Database – Simplified View

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam rectangle {
  BorderColor #000000
  BorderThickness 1
}

rectangle "Enrollment Database (Postgres)" as ENROLLMENT_DB {
  rectangle "Academic Structure\n(courses, sections, majors, minors)" as ACADEMIC
  rectangle "Requirements\n(major/minor/concentration requirements)" as REQUIREMENTS
  rectangle "Enrollment & Scheduling\n(enrollments, deadlines, conflicts)" as ENROLLMENT
  rectangle "Financial Data\n(tuition, fees, costs, housing)" as FINANCIAL
  rectangle "Transfer Data\n(institutions, courses, equivalencies)" as TRANSFER
  rectangle "People\n(students, instructors)" as PEOPLE
}

cloud "Enrollment Service" as ENROLLMENT_SVC

ENROLLMENT_SVC --> ACADEMIC
ENROLLMENT_SVC --> REQUIREMENTS
ENROLLMENT_SVC --> ENROLLMENT
ENROLLMENT_SVC --> FINANCIAL
ENROLLMENT_SVC --> TRANSFER
ENROLLMENT_SVC --> PEOPLE

note right of ENROLLMENT_SVC
**Key Use Cases:**
- Course search & section lookup
- Degree audit & requirements
- Budget calculation
- Transfer equivalency
- Schedule optimization
end note

@enduml

